Interactive Fan README
This is a simple interactive fan animation built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Click the fan to turn it on and off.

Features
Interactive: Click the fan to toggle its movement.

Visual: Smooth animation simulates a rotating fan.

Lightweight: Built with fundamental web technologies.

Technologies Used
HTML5: Structures the fan's components.

CSS3: Styles the fan and provides the animation.

JavaScript: Handles the click event to start and stop the animation.

How to Use
Open the file: Simply open the index.html file in your web browser.

Interact: Click the fan to see it spin!

File Structure
index.html: The main HTML file containing the structure.

style.css: The CSS file for styling and animation.

script.js: The JavaScript file for interactivity.
